token_info.name: The Big Odd
token_info.description: Signed Digital Vinyl of the band The Big Odd. The Brazilian instrumental quintet composed by Gabriel Perpétuo, Vicente França, Tiago Eiras, Antônio Vinícius Silva and Guilherme Peluci, released their debut album on November 8th 2020 – a sonic mix of post-rock, progressive music and jazz that places high value on freedom, creativity, and self-expression. Listen to the full album at https://thebigodd.bandcamp.com/album/the-big-odd. 100/100 copies.
